                <div type="transcription">
<p>[On the geological work of Tschudi and Buch.] ‘… My health keeps indifferent &amp; I do not suppose I shall ever be a strong man again: everything fatigues me, &amp; I can work but little at my writing: this summer, however, I shall get out my geology of S America …</p>
<p>I found Bronns Geschichte,<ref target="#foot.f2"/> which you recommended me, very useful, for references to facts on variation …’</p> 
                </div>
